BACKUP ~weidu_external/k0_iskp/backup~
SUPPORT ~https://www.gibberlings3.net/forums/forum/214-sod-to-bg2ee-item-upgrade/~
AUTO_EVAL_STRINGS
VERSION ~v4.0.0-BETA~
README ~k0_iskp/readme.md~

ASK_EVERY_COMPONENT

AUTO_TRA ~k0_iskp/lang/%s~
ALWAYS
  INCLUDE ~k0_iskp/lib/functions.tpa~
END

LANGUAGE  ~English~
          ~english~
          ~k0_iskp/lang/english/weidu.tra~

